Package: fb4package
Type: Package
Title: Fish Bioenergetics 4.0 Model Implementation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Hans", "Ttito",
      email = "kvttitos@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: An R implementation of fish bioenergetics modeling based on Fish Bioenergetics 4.0 (Deslauriers et al., 2017). Provides automated parameter optimization, multi-prey diet modeling, and comprehensive energy budget simulations for fisheries research and aquaculture applications. The package includes species-specific parameter databases and tools for modeling fish growth, consumption, and metabolism under varying environmental conditions.
